## Elementor REST API (2026-03-22)

mu-plugin: `sk-elementor-write.php` (deployed 2026-03-22)
Requires: `manage_options` capability (admin app password)

| Endpoint | Method | Source |
|----------|--------|--------|
| `/sk/v1/elementor/{id}` | GET | sk-elementor-api.php |
| `/sk/v1/elementor/{id}/replace` | POST | sk-elementor-api.php |
| `/sk/v1/elementor/{id}/backup` | GET | sk-elementor-api.php |
| `/sk/v1/elementor/{id}/restore` | POST | sk-elementor-api.php |
| `/sk/v1/elementor/{id}/write` | POST | sk-elementor-write.php |

Write endpoint auto-creates `_elementor_data_backup` before overwrite.

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-23-RnhgSdeLtVw_2026-03-23-19-03.md -->

