### PATTERN — Мониторинг ресурсов

Check Claude Code subscription limits regularly, plan token usage, consider premium for intensive use, test gradually.

## Distilled 2026-03-24

### Path Facts

- **youtube-notes correct path**: `youtube-notes/` (vault root) — the folder `30-Resources/Learning/video-notes/` was a blank duplicate causing path confusion; deleted 2026-03-22. All Nexus configs and workflow nodes must reference `youtube-notes/`. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

### NGG Gallery Integration Method

- **Preferred integration order** (Elementor safety, descending priority): <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->
  1. Shortcode widget (`[ngg src="galleries" ids="X" display="basic_thumbnail"]`) — safest, editor-friendly
  2. Direct `post_content` insertion via API — use when Elementor is not active on page
  3. Elementor visual widget — last resort; WYSIWYG constraints cause rendering conflicts
- **Rationale**: Elementor hybrid rendering makes direct widget placement fragile when `post_content` and `_elementor_data` meta coexist. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

